msgstr "当二进制文件优雅关闭时，将写入配置文件数据。如果没有进行优化构建，请检查这一点："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-25-native-pgo.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`default.iprof` exists in `target/` after tests run"
msgstr "测试运行后， `target/` 中存在 `default.iprof`"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-25-native-pgo.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Your tests actually start the application (check test logs)"
msgstr "您的测试确实启动了应用程序（检查测试日志）"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-25-native-pgo.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The instrumented binary shut down cleanly (a crash or `SIGKILL` prevents the profile from being written)"
msgstr "被检测二进制文件干净利落地关闭（崩溃或 `SIGKILL` 会阻止写入配置文件）"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-25-native-pgo.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Enable verbose logging to see what's happening:"
msgstr "启用详细日志记录，查看发生了什么："

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-25-native-pgo.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Build fails with \"PGO requires Oracle GraalVM\""
msgstr "构建失败，提示 \"PGO 需要 Oracle GraalVM\"。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-25-native-pgo.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "You're using a GraalVM distribution that doesn't support PGO. Download Oracle GraalVM from https://www.oracle.com/java/technologies/downloads/#graalvmjava25[oracle.com] or use SDKMAN:"
msgstr "您使用的 GraalVM 发行版不支持 PGO。请从 link:https://www.oracle.com/java/technologies/downloads/#graalvmjava25[oracle.com] 下载 Oracle GraalVM 或使用 SDKMAN："

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-25-native-pgo.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Optimized binary is slower"
msgstr "优化后的二进制文件速度更慢"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
